Carefully remove egg yolk from eggs and place in mixing bowl and mash. To the yolks, add Dannon(R) All Natural Plain Yogurt, mustard, curry powder, hot sauce, green onion and celery. Mash together and mix well. Taste filling and add salt to taste. Add more hot sauce, if desired, for spicier eggs. Use a spoon or pastry bag to fill egg whites with yolk mixture.